ue, "45": true}, "8": {}}, "myGroups": ["4", "5", "6", "7"], "sessionId": "sess_1778254521808_rci8m8gmedh", "answers": {"1": "Hipokrat Yemini", "2": "D", "3": "Esaretin Bedeli / The Shawshank Redemption", "4": "C", "5": "Sefiller", "6": "B", "7": "Kafadanbacakl\u0131lar", "8": "D", "9": "Sultan Abd\u00fclaziz", "10": "B", "11": "Hababam S\u0131n\u0131f\u0131", "12": "Sherlock", "13": "Recep \u0130vedik", "14": "Modern Family", "15": "\u0130kinci Bahar", "16": "Geli\u015f/Arrival", "17": "K\u0131rg\u0131n \u00c7i\u00e7ekler", "18": "Kuzular\u0131n Sessizli\u011fi/The Silence of the Lambs", "19": "K\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 Oda", "20": "Guguk Ku\u015fu/One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest", "21": "1-2-3", "22": "1-4", "23": "2-3-4", "24": "3-4", "25": "2-3", "26": "Michelin", "27": "D", "28": "Tinker Bell", "29": "C", "30": "J\u00fcl Sezar/Julius Caesar", "31": "C", "32": "Ven\u00fcs ve Uran\u00fcs", "33": "B", "34": "Roland-Garros/Fransa A\u00e7\u0131k", "35": "A", "41": "D", "42": "G\u00fcney Afrika", "43": "Edirne,Tekirda\u011f,K\u0131rklareli (\u0130stanbul (Avrupa),\u00c7anakkale (Avrupa) k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131n\u0131 kapsar ama tamam\u0131 deniliyor soruda bu y\u00fczden bunlar\u0131 baz almad\u0131k)", "44": "Nepal", "45": "Paris"}, "answersFile": "Pub Olimpiyatlar\u0131 38.docx (40 cevap) (40 cevap) (40 cevap) (40 cevap) (40 cevap)", "questions": {"1": {"question": "Antik Yunan d\u00f6neminde ya\u015fam\u0131\u015f ve \"T\u0131bb\u0131n Babas\u0131\" olarak kabul edilen hekimin ad\u0131yla an\u0131lan; hekimlerin mesleklerini icra ederken etik de\u011ferlere ba\u011fl\u0131 kalacaklar\u0131na dair ettikleri tarihi ba\u011fl\u0131l\u0131k metninin ad\u0131 nedir?", "answer": "Hipokrat Yemini", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "2": {"question": "Ormanda kayboldu\u011funuzu hayal edin.\u00c7ad\u0131r\u2019\u0131n\u0131z sizin o an bulundu\u011funuz noktan\u0131n g\u00fcneydo\u011fusun\u2019da kal\u0131yor. Elinizde ise bir pusula var.Pusula\u2019y\u0131 takip ederek \u00e7ad\u0131r\u0131n\u0131za ula\u015fmak i\u00e7in hangi harfleri takip etmeniz gerekmektedir?\nA)NE B)SW C)NW D)SE", "answer": "D", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "3": {"question": "3 milyonu a\u015fk\u0131n oy ve 9.3'l\u00fck puan\u0131 ile yakla\u015f\u0131k 20 y\u0131l\u0131 a\u015fk\u0131n s\u00fcredir IMDB Top 250 listesinin 1 numaral\u0131 yap\u0131m olarak kalmay\u0131 ba\u015farm\u0131\u015f olan film hangi filmdir?", "answer": "Esaretin Bedeli / The Shawshank Redemption", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "4": {"question": "\u00c7imsa \u00c7BK Mersin tak\u0131m\u0131 ge\u00e7ti\u011fimiz g\u00fcnlerde Avrupa\u2019da kupa kazanan ilk Anadolu tak\u0131m\u0131 olmay\u0131 ba\u015farm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r.Peki \u00c7imsa \u00c7BK Mersin hangi alanda kupa kazanarak bu ilki ger\u00e7ekle\u015ftirmi\u015ftir?\nA)Futbol B)Voleybol C)Basketbol D)Hentbol", "answer": "C", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "5": {"question": "A\u00e7 ye\u011fenlerini doyurmak i\u00e7in bir somun ekmek \u00e7ald\u0131\u011f\u0131nda k\u00fcrek cezas\u0131na \u00e7arpt\u0131r\u0131lan ve ka\u00e7ma giri\u015fimleriyle y\u0131llarca hapiste kalan; \u00f6zg\u00fcrl\u00fc\u011f\u00fcne kavu\u015ftuktan sonra bir piskoposun merhametiyle hayat\u0131n\u0131 iyili\u011fe adayan karakter hangi roman\u0131n ba\u015f kahraman\u0131d\u0131r?", "answer": "Sefiller", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "6": {"question": "F\u0131rat ve Dicle nehirleri aras\u0131nda yer alan ve \u201cmedeniyetlerin be\u015fi\u011fi\u201d olarak an\u0131lan Mezopotamya, bir\u00e7ok uygarl\u0131\u011fa ev sahipli\u011fi yapm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Peki, tarihte bilinen ilk imparatorluk, ilk d\u00fczenli ordu ve ilk merkezi y\u00f6netim \u00f6rneklerini olu\u015fturan Kral Sargon\u2019un devleti hangi uygarl\u0131kt\u0131r?\nA)S\u00fcmerler B)Akadlar C)Babiller D)Asurlular", "answer": "B", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "7": {"question": "Genellikle tuzlu sularda ya\u015fayan; geli\u015fmi\u015f sinir sistemleri, birden fazla kalbe sahip olma ve mavi kan gibi \u00f6zellikleriyle dikkat \u00e7eken, yumu\u015fak\u00e7alar \u015fubesinin evrimsel a\u00e7\u0131dan en geli\u015fmi\u015f s\u0131n\u0131f\u0131na ne ad verilir?", "answer": "Kafadanbacakl\u0131lar", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "8": {"question": "\u00c7aykovski'nin besteledi\u011fi son bale olan F\u0131nd\u0131kk\u0131ran\u2019da yer alan \u201c\u015eeker Perisi\u2019nin Dans\u0131\u201d b\u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fc, b\u00fcy\u00fcl\u00fc ve masals\u0131 t\u0131n\u0131s\u0131yla dikkat \u00e7eker. Peki dinleyecek olaca\u011f\u0131n\u0131z bu b\u00f6l\u00fcmde duyulan karakteristik ses hangi enstr\u00fcmana aittir?\nA)Timpani B)Synthesizer C)Marimba D)\u00c7elesta", "answer": "D", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "9": {"question": "Osmanl\u0131 saray mutfa\u011f\u0131 ile Frans\u0131z mutfa\u011f\u0131n\u0131 birle\u015ftiren bir f\u00fczyon yeme\u011fi olan ve hikayesinin ard\u0131nda h\u00fcz\u00fcnl\u00fc bir a\u015fk hikayesini saklayan 'H\u00fcnkar Be\u011fendi',  hangi padi\u015fah\u0131n be\u011fenisi \u00fczerine bu isimle an\u0131lm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r?", "answer": "Sultan Abd\u00fclaziz", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "10": {"question": "Sokaklar\u0131nda en \u00e7ok 54 plaka ara\u00e7lar\u0131 g\u00f6rd\u00fc\u011f\u00fcn\u00fcz bir \u015fehrin en \u00fcnl\u00fc y\u00f6resel \u00fcr\u00fcn\u00fc nedir? (Plaka numaras\u0131 54 olan ilimizin en \u00fcnl\u00fc y\u00f6resel lezzetini ar\u0131yoruz)\nA)Bafra pidesi B)Islama k\u00f6fte C)Testi kebab\u0131 D)Perde pilav\u0131", "answer": "B", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 1"}, "11": {"question": "\u00d6zel bir lisede \u00f6\u011frenim g\u00f6ren haylaz \u00f6\u011frenciler toplulu\u011fu, yeni atanan disiplinli m\u00fcd\u00fcr muavinini s\u00fcrekli k\u0131\u015fk\u0131rtarak yaramaz planlar yapar. \u00d6zetledi\u011fimiz bu film hangi filmdir?", "answer": "Hababam S\u0131n\u0131f\u0131", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "12": {"question": "G\u00f6rselde g\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f oldu\u011funuz karakter, hangi dizinin karakterdir?", "answer": "Sherlock", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "13": {"question": "G\u00f6rseldeki film objesi hangi filme aittir?", "answer": "Recep \u0130vedik", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "14": {"question": "Dinlemi\u015f oldu\u011funuz \u015fark\u0131 hangi diziye aittir?", "answer": "Modern Family", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "15": {"question": "G\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f oldu\u011funuz sahne kesiti hangi diziye aittir?", "answer": "\u0130kinci Bahar", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "16": {"question": "D\u00fcnyan\u0131n 12 farkl\u0131 noktas\u0131na devasa, gizemli uzay ara\u00e7lar\u0131 iner. ABD ordusu, bu varl\u0131klar\u0131n amac\u0131n\u0131 \u00f6\u011frenmek i\u00e7in bir dilbilimci ve bir fizik\u00e7iyi g\u00f6revlendirir. \u00d6zetledi\u011fimiz bu film hangi filmdir?", "answer": "Geli\u015f/Arrival", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "17": {"question": "G\u00f6rselde g\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f oldu\u011funuz karakter, hangi dizinin karakterdir?", "answer": "K\u0131rg\u0131n \u00c7i\u00e7ekler", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "18": {"question": "G\u00f6rseldeki film objesi hangi filme aittir?", "answer": "Kuzular\u0131n Sessizli\u011fi/The Silence of the Lambs", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "19": {"question": "Dinlemi\u015f oldu\u011funuz \u015fark\u0131 hangi diziye aittir?", "answer": "K\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 Oda", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "20": {"question": "G\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f oldu\u011funuz sahne kesiti hangi filme aittir?", "answer": "Guguk Ku\u015fu/One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest", "section": "Ekran Av\u0131"}, "21": {"question": "Hangisi/leri T\u00fcrkiye\u2019nin en y\u00fcksek n\u00fcfuslu ilk 3 ilinden birinin telefon alan kodlar\u0131 aras\u0131ndad\u0131r?\n1-216 2-232 3-312 4-326", "answer": "1-2-3", "section": "Hangisi?"}, "22": {"question": "Hangisi/leri TDK\u2019ye g\u00f6re do\u011fru yaz\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olan kelimelerdendir?\n1-Gl\u00fcten 2-S\u00fcliet 3-\u015eovalye4-Trambolin", "answer": "1-4", "section": "Hangisi?"}, "23": {"question": "Hangisi/leri Batman'in en b\u00fcy\u00fck d\u00fc\u015fman\u0131 olan 'Joker' karakterini canland\u0131rm\u0131\u015f olan \u00fcnl\u00fc akt\u00f6rlerdendir?\n1-Nicolas Cage 2-Jack Nicholson 3- Jared Leto  4- Heath Ledger", "answer": "2-3-4", "section": "Hangisi?"}, "24": {"question": "Hangisi/leri eser ve yazar/sanat\u00e7\u0131 olarak do\u011fru bir \u015fekilde e\u015fle\u015ftirilmi\u015ftir?\n1-\u015eair Evlenmesi- Nam\u0131k Kemal  2-Davut-Raphael 3- Serg\u00fcze\u015ft-Samipa\u015fazade Sezai  4- D\u00fc\u015f\u00fcnen Adam- Auguste Rodin", "answer": "3-4", "section": "Hangisi?"}, "25": {"question": "Hangisi/leri do\u011fru bir bilgidir?\n1-Mars\u2019\u0131n k\u0131z\u0131l renkte olmas\u0131n\u0131n nedeni y\u00fczeyinin \u00e7ok y\u00fcksek s\u0131cakl\u0131kta olmas\u0131d\u0131r.\n2-Flamingolar\u0131n t\u00fcy renklerinin zamanla de\u011fi\u015fmesinin sebebi beslenme \u015fekilleriyle ilgidir.\n3-FIFA D\u00fcnya Kupas\u0131nda en \u00e7ok gol atan futbolcu Miroslav Klose\u2019dir.\n4- Boya \u00e7al\u0131\u015fmalar\u0131nda t\u00fcm ana renklerin kar\u0131\u015f\u0131m\u0131ndan beyaz renk elde edilir.", "answer": "2-3", "section": "Hangisi?"}, "26": {"question": "Bir otomobil lasti\u011fi \u00fcreticisi taraf\u0131ndan s\u00fcr\u00fcc\u00fclerin seyahatlerinin kolayla\u015ft\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131 ve lastik sat\u0131\u015flar\u0131n\u0131n artt\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131 ad\u0131na olu\u015fturulan \u00fccretsiz bir rehber; bug\u00fcn g\u00fcn\u00fcm\u00fczde otel mutfaklar\u0131na ve restoranlara verilen bir prestij \u00f6d\u00fcl\u00fc haline gelmi\u015ftir diyen bir ki\u015fi hangi markadan bahsetmektedir?", "answer": "Michelin", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "27": {"question": "G\u00fczellik sekt\u00f6r\u00fcne ad\u0131m atan \u00fcnl\u00fc isimler, kendi markalar\u0131yla da dikkat \u00e7ekmektedir.\nPeki, \u015f\u0131klardaki \u00fcnl\u00fc isim\u2013marka e\u015fle\u015ftirmelerinden hangisi yanl\u0131\u015ft\u0131r?\nA) Rihanna \u2013 Fenty Beauty\nB) Selena Gomez \u2013 Rare Beauty\nC) Kylie Jenner \u2013 Kylie Cosmetics\nD) Hailey Bieber \u2013 Florence by Hails", "answer": "D", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "28": {"question": "\u0130sko\u00e7 bir yazar taraf\u0131ndan yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olan, sonsuz \u00e7ocuklu\u011funu Varolmayan \u00dclke adl\u0131 b\u00fcy\u00fcl\u00fc bir adada, Kay\u0131p \u00c7ocuklar \u00e7etesinin lideri olarak maceralar ya\u015fayarak ge\u00e7iren masal kahraman\u0131n\u0131n peri arkada\u015f\u0131 kimdir?", "answer": "Tinker Bell", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "29": {"question": "Psikoloji tarihinin en tart\u0131\u015fmal\u0131 deneylerinden biri olan \u201cK\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck Albert\u201d deneyinde, korkunun klasik ko\u015fullanma yoluyla \u00f6\u011frenilip \u00f6\u011frenilemeyece\u011fi incelenmi\u015f, Albert, ona g\u00f6t\u00fcr\u00fclen canl\u0131ya her dokundu\u011funda y\u00fcksek bir sesle korkutulmu\u015f, canl\u0131ya kar\u015f\u0131 zamanla korku geli\u015ftirmi\u015f ve bu korku benzer nesnelere de genellenmi\u015ftir. Peki, bu deneyde Albert\u2019\u0131n yan\u0131na g\u00f6t\u00fcr\u00fclen canl\u0131 neydi?\nA)Siyah k\u00f6pek B)Siyah kedi C)Beyaz fare D)Beyaz tav\u015fan", "answer": "C", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "30": {"question": "D\u00f6neminin politikac\u0131s\u0131 seyahat ederken korsanlar taraf\u0131ndan esir al\u0131n\u0131r ve korsanlar fidye tutar\u0131 belirledi\u011finde politikac\u0131 fidye tutar\u0131n\u0131 be\u011fenmez ve 2 kat artt\u0131r\u0131lmas\u0131n\u0131 s\u00f6yler. 38 g\u00fcn sonra serbest kald\u0131\u011f\u0131nda ise korsanlar\u0131 Bergama\u2019da idam ettirir. D\u00f6neminin en \u00f6nemli isimlerinden olan bu ki\u015fi kimdir?", "answer": "J\u00fcl Sezar/Julius Caesar", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "31": {"question": "Rushmore Da\u011f\u0131 An\u0131t\u0131 ABD\u2019nin en b\u00fcy\u00fck sembollerinden biridir ve ABD\u2019nin ikon haline gelmi\u015f ba\u015fkanlar\u0131ndan 4\u2019\u00fcn\u00fcn sil\u00fcetini i\u00e7ermektedir.Peki \u015f\u0131klardaki hangi isim bu an\u0131tta yer alan ba\u015fkanlardan biri de\u011fildir?\nA)Thomas Jefferson B)George Washington C)Harry Truman D)Theodore Roosevelt", "answer": "C", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "32": {"question": "G\u00fcne\u015f Sistemi\u2019nde \u00e7o\u011fu gezegen kendi ekseni etraf\u0131nda ayn\u0131 y\u00f6nde d\u00f6nerken, iki gezegen adeta \u201ckurallar\u0131 bozarak\u201d ters y\u00f6nde d\u00f6nmektedir.\nBu al\u0131\u015f\u0131lmad\u0131k d\u00f6n\u00fc\u015fe sahip gezegenler hangileridir?", "answer": "Ven\u00fcs ve Uran\u00fcs", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "33": {"question": "Yazarlar, y\u0131llardan beri i\u00e7inde ya\u015fad\u0131klar\u0131 toplumlar\u0131n tarihlerini eserlerine konu olarak se\u00e7mi\u015f, T\u00fcrk edebiyat\u0131nda ise \u00f6zellikle Kurtulu\u015f Sava\u015f\u0131\u2019n\u0131n izleri eserlere yans\u0131m\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. \u015e\u0131klardaki romanlardan hangisi bu izleri ta\u015f\u0131yan bir esere \u00f6rnek de\u011fildir?\nA) Vurun Kahpeye B)Devlet Ana C)Sodom ve Gomore D)K\u00fc\u00e7\u00fck A\u011fa", "answer": "B", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "34": {"question": "Her y\u0131l May\u0131s ay\u0131nda d\u00fczenlenen turnuva 4 d\u00fcnya Grand Slam turnuvas\u0131ndan ikincisidir.1891 y\u0131l\u0131ndan beri d\u00fczenlenen bu turnuva toprak (kil)zeminde d\u00fczenlenmektedir.Bahsedilen bu turnuvan\u0131n ad\u0131 nedir?", "answer": "Roland-Garros/Fransa A\u00e7\u0131k", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "35": {"question": "Claude Monet\u2019nin 1872 y\u0131l\u0131nda resmetti\u011fi \u201cG\u00fcn Do\u011fumu\u201d tablosu, bir sanat ak\u0131m\u0131n\u0131n ilk \u00f6rne\u011fi olarak kabul edilmi\u015f ve bu ak\u0131ma ismini vermi\u015ftir. Peki bu tablo hangi sanat ak\u0131m\u0131na ismini vermi\u015ftir?\nA)Empresyonizm B)Realizm C)Dadaizm D)Ekspresyonizm", "answer": "A", "section": "Trivia Quiz Part 2"}, "36": {"question": "Marilyn Monroe", "answer": "", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "37": {"question": "\u0130rfan De\u011firmenci", "answer": "", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "38": {"question": "Paul McCartney", "answer": "", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "39": {"question": "Yasemin Yal\u00e7\u0131n", "answer": "", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "40": {"question": "Z\u00fclf\u00fc Livaneli\nDevri Alem", "answer": "", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "41": {"question": "Gize Piramitleri, Kahire yak\u0131nlar\u0131nda in\u015fa edilen, \u00fc\u00e7 ana an\u0131t mezardan olu\u015fan yap\u0131lar toplulu\u011fudur. \u015e\u0131klardan hangisi bu \u00fc\u00e7 ana piramitten biri de\u011fildir?\nA)Keops  B)Kefren C)Mikerinos D)Sifertios", "answer": "D", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "42": {"question": "Ekranda g\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f oldu\u011funuz bayrak hangi \u00fclkenin bayra\u011f\u0131d\u0131r?", "answer": "G\u00fcney Afrika", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "43": {"question": "\u00dclkemizin s\u0131n\u0131rlar\u0131 i\u00e7erisinde bulunan Do\u011fu Trakya b\u00f6lgesi hangi illerimizin tamam\u0131n\u0131 kapsamaktad\u0131r?", "answer": "Edirne,Tekirda\u011f,K\u0131rklareli (\u0130stanbul (Avrupa),\u00c7anakkale (Avrupa) k\u0131s\u0131mlar\u0131n\u0131 kapsar ama tamam\u0131 deniliyor soruda bu y\u00fczden bunlar\u0131 baz almad\u0131k)", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "44": {"question": "Bayra\u011f\u0131nda bir g\u00fcne\u015f ve bir ay simgesi bulunan \u00fclke resmi olarak g\u00fcne\u015f y\u0131l\u0131na dayal\u0131 Bikram Sambat takvimini kulland\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan dolay\u0131 miladi takvimden 56 y\u0131l 8 ay \u00f6ndedir ve bundan dolay\u0131 resmi olarak 2083 y\u0131l\u0131na girmi\u015ftir. Bahsedilen \u00fclke hangi \u00fclkedir?", "answer": "Nepal", "section": "Bluru Netle"}, "45": {"question": "Ekranda g\u00f6rm\u00fc\u015f oldu\u011funuz ikonik yap\u0131n\u0131n bulundu\u011fu \u00fclkenin ba\u015fkenti neresidir?", "answer": "Paris", "section": "Blur